</LP>
<TEXT>
   ("Annual golf-course maintenance is at a record of $27,744
a hole. . . ." -- WSJ news item)
                                                                                                       

   It seems like a lot of money
   To take care of a piece of earth,
   But for the time spent on each hole
   I am getting my money's worth.
   -- Arnold J. Zarett.
   ---
   Working Mother
                                                                                                       

   Juggling two jobs isn't easy. This morning she got the
kids out of bed and before she knew it, she had dressed, fed,
collated and stapled them]
   -- Robert Orben.
