</IN>
<LP>
   SEOUL -- Disgruntled stock investors, shouting "Down with
{President} Roh Tae-woo," demonstrated Friday to protest the
lack of government measures to boost the sagging South Korean
market, witnesses said.
   Police said they arrested eight protesters.
</LP>
