marketing problems since it was acquired by Suchard for $730
million in 1987. In 1986, Brach had pretax profit of about
$75 million, on sales of about $462 million; in 1989, it had
a $50 million operating loss. Suchard has annual profit of
about 275 million francs ($48.7 million).
